modName: UNP Conversion Dark Ebony Valkyrie Armour
summary: Simple UNP Conversion of this great armour.
descriptionHtml:
** Description **
This is UNP not UNPB BBP or some HDT variant, so you wont have butt/breast physics on it.

** Requirements**
- UNP body.

You are free to realease any bug fixes for this mod as long as you give credits to the original author [b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1259781/?]comrade1280[/url][/b] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/16229004]Alunder[/url] who made the CBBE version for the armour and me for the first UNP conversion. 

You can visit the original mod's page here through this link: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49953/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49953/?[/url]
You can see CBBE version here: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67420/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67420/?[/url]

Credits to:
[b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1259781/?]comrade1280[/url][/b] for the armour.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/16229004]Alunder[/url] for the CBBE version which I converted to UNP.
